Ising model in two dimensions with periodic boundary conditions
Libraries include:
  -- heat-bath updating methods on full and subattices
  -- Wolff cluster updating on full and sublattice
  -- functions for coarse-graining lattices
  -- function for refining lattices

Test programs are located in the tests directory, production programs are located in the porduction directory.

To compile. enter into a test or production subdirectory, e.g.,

cd tests/interpolator

and run:

../../make.sh main.C

